We are grateful to our sponsors.  Amazing Diva is a non-profit organization designed to celebrate the courageous women who, while battling cancer, still look after their families and responsibilities.   Monthly, Amazing Diza performs complimentary total make offers for cancer patients.  The diva crowing comes along with a coronation that is celebrated with family and friends!  Want to know how it work?  Learn more at www.amazingdiva.org

Chicago Undercover is proud to partner with Amazing Diva's.  We all know a diva that has stood proud during their battle.
